Package: sensor-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Tools for managing and reading sensor data
 This package provides command-line tools for working with sensor data.
 .
 Features include:
  * Command-line tools for sensor interaction
  * JSON/CSV transformer for sensor data files
  * Support for processing multiple files and directories
  * sensor-mon: ncurses-based sensor monitoring interface
  * sensor-plot: historical sensor data graphing tool
